# Border Options Test
# Tests BorderRadius, BorderColor, BorderWidth, and Padding
Output examples/svgs/border-test.svg

Set Width 600
Set Height 300
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme dark
Set Title "Border Test"
Set BorderRadius 20
Set BorderWidth 3
Set BorderColor #ff5555
Set Padding 32

Type "Testing border options"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "BorderRadius: 20, BorderWidth: 3"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "BorderColor: #ff5555, Padding: 32"
Sleep 1s
